<div id="div1"class="p-4 bg-gray-100 border border-gray-300 rounded">
    <h2 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Integrative Medicine</h2>
    <p class="text-lg mb-4">
        Integrative Medicine is evidence-based healthcare that focuses on treating the whole person. It can be described as a practice that “Cherry Picks” the best and scientifically supported therapies of both systems. The ultimate goal: to treat the patients better, through the use of safe, effective, and less-invasive interventions whenever possible.
        <a href="https://www.who.int/news/item/19-08-2023-global-partners-commit-to-advance-evidence-based-traditional--complementary-and-integrative-medicine" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Read more...</a>
    </p>
</div>

