<section class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 p-4">
    <!-- Top Left -->
    <div class="p-4 bg-gray-100 border border-gray-300 rounded">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Treat Root Cause Not Only Symptoms</h2>
        <p class="text-lg mb-4">At HH Non-Surgical Hospital, we focus on the root cause, not only symptoms. We employ techniques that are carefully curated to complement the body's biological processes. These may include targeted interventions, rehabilitative exercises, and lifestyle modifications designed to support and amplify the body's natural healing responses.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Top Right -->
    <div class="flex items-center justify-center bg-gray-100 border border-gray-300 rounded">
