        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">With Team, Focus on Whole Person</h2>
        <p class="text-lg mb-4">Integrative Healthcare focuses on the whole person. Integrative medicine includes all providers of integrative medicine - working in equal partnership for the better of the patient - nurses, medical doctors, naturopathic doctors, chiropractic doctors, acupuncture and oriental medicine doctors, and many more. The ultimate goal: to treat the patients better, through the use of safe, effective, and less-invasive interventions.</p>
    </div>
